            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>深圳职工二档和居民参保人在这里也能刷医保了！但这点要注意】宝子们！深圳职工二档和居民参保人，在深圳大学附属华南医院就诊，也能享受普通门诊统筹待遇啦<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[送花花]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/cb/2022_Flowers_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>主打一个省心省钱！⚠️但宝子们注意，要先在选定的医疗机构办理门诊转诊手续哦！对于这个消息，大家可能还有这2个疑问，卫子来一一解答👇🏻<br><br>- 深圳职工二档、居民医保参保人，能享受吗？<br>- 转诊后的职工二档和居民医保在该院的报销比例是多少？👉🏻<a href="https://weibo.cn/sinaurl?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2Fa_igO2gVHxD-UHFNVrynFw" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">华南医保 | 好消息！这些人来华南医院看病也能刷医保啦！</span></a>  <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%96%B0%E9%B2%9C%E4%BA%8B%E5%84%BF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%96%B0%E9%B2%9C%E4%BA%8B%E5%84%BF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫新鲜事儿#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjq3ago1syj20c60lfmze.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjq3agp2vcj20c20lgdhx.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
